  "statement": "Clear failure when the session is unreachable. If the target session cannot be reached (no session, dead process, broken bridge), the app SHALL show a clear, plain-English failure and SHALL NOT silently drop the message. - *Acceptance:* With no reachable session, sending a message produces a visible failure message naming what went wrong and what to do; no message is shown as \"sent\" when it was not delivered",
